<div hand="#CL" n="CL">

<!-- p.503, Missionary Travels, sh -->
<pb facs="liv_000101_0152.jpg" n="0152"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><note place="inspace above" hand="#U1" rend="gray">P. 503-532</note> <fw><add place="inspace" hand="#U1" rend="gray right">147</add></fw>
<lb/><note place="inline" hand="#DL" n="DL">XLVII</note> So <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">in accordance with <choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> advice <choice><abbr>`</abbr><expan>of</expan></choice> my <term type="tribe">Libonta</term> friends</add> I did not fail to reprove <add place="inline" hand="#DL" n="DL">"</add>my child <subst><del type="cancelled" hand="#DL" n="DL">on this <unclear cert="low">but</unclear></del><add place="above" hand="#DL" n="DL"><persName>Sekeletu</persName>"</add></subst>
<lb/>for his marauding <del type="strikethrough" hand="#DL" n="DL">acts</del> <space extent="2" unit="chars"/>This was not done in an angry manner
<lb/>for no <subst><del><gap extent="4" unit="chars"/></del><add place="over-text" hand="#DL" n="DL">good</add></subst> is ever achieved by fierce denunciation <space extent="3" unit="chars"/><persName><choice><orig>Motib<subst><del hand="#DL" n="DL">a</del><add place="over-text" hand="#DL" n="DL">e</add></subst></orig><reg>Motibe</reg></choice></persName><del type="cancelled" hand="#DL" n="DL">'s</del>
<lb/><del type="cancelled">fat</del> his father in law said to me "Scold him much but <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice>
<lb/>let others hear you". </p>
<lb/><p><space extent="20" unit="chars"/>The <term type="tribe">Makololo</term> expressed great
<lb/>satisfaction with <choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> route <metamark function="insertion" resp="#DL" n="DL"/><anchor xml:id="reorder-99"/> to the West <metamark function="reorder" resp="#DL" n="DL" spanTo="#meta-235"/><seg corresp="#reorder-99"> we had opened up</seg><anchor xml:id="meta-235"/>
<lb/>and soon after our arrival a <foreign xml:lang="tn">Picho</foreign> was called in order to discuss
<lb/><choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> question of removal to <choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> <placeName><geogName type="valley">Barotse valley</geogName></placeName> <del type="strikethrough">in order</del> <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">so that they might</add> <del type="cancelled">to</del> be nearer
<lb/><choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> market <space extent="3" unit="chars"/>Some of <choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> older men objected to abandoning <choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> line
<lb/><choice><abbr>`</abbr><expan>of</expan></choice> defence afforded by <choice><abbr>'</abbr><expan>the</expan></choice> <del type="strikethrough">river</del> <placeName><geogName type="river">Chobe</geogName></placeName> and <placeName><geogName type="river"><choice><orig>Zambesi</orig><reg>Zambezi</reg></choice></geogName></placeName> against their
<lb/>southern enemies the <term type="tribe">Matebele</term> <space extent="3" unit="chars"/>The <term type="tribe">Makololo</term> <add place="below" hand="#DL" n="DL">^</add> <add place="above" hand="#DL" n="DL">generally</add> have

</p>

</div>
            
<!-- sample div in DL's hand with additions by Charles. -->
            <div hand="#DL" n="DL">

<pb facs="liv_000101_0155.jpg" n="0155"/>
<lb/><p><space dim="vertical" extent="10" unit="lines"/>
<lb/><space extent="25" unit="chars"/><add place="inline" corresp="#add-26">or least fatal</add>
<lb/><space dim="vertical" extent="10" unit="lines"/>
<lb/><space extent="40" unit="chars"/><add place="inline" corresp="#add-27">either</add>
<lb/>more lines in Livingstone's hand...
<lb/>more lines written in Livingstone hand...
<lb/>more lines written in Livingstone hand...
<lb/>more lines written in Livingstone hand...</p>


<pb facs="liv_000101_0156.jpg" n="0156"/><!-- DL div continues -->
<lb/><fw><add place="inspace" hand="#U1" rend="gray right">149</add></fw>
<lb/><p>I believe that the <placeName><region>Interior</region></placeName> of this country presents a
<lb/>much more inviting field for the <term type="occupation">Philanthropist</term>
<lb/>than does the West coast where <term type="occupation">missionaries</term>
<lb/>of the <orgName><choice><sic>church missionary</sic><corr>Church Missionary</corr></choice></orgName> <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above"><orgName>United Presbyterian</orgName></add> &amp; other societies have
<lb/>long laboured with <del type="cancelled">the</del> most <subst><del type="cancelled">marvellous</del><add place="above">astonishing</add></subst> <w>devoted<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>ness</w> and <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">never flagging</add> zeal - There the <term type="ailment">fevers</term> are much
<lb/>more virulent <del type="cancelled"><subst><del>than</del><add place="over-text">and</add></subst></del> <add place="above">&amp;</add> more speedily fatal
<lb/><add hand="#CL" n="CL" place="above">Some words added by Charles Livingstone</add> <del type="strikethrough" hand="#CL" n="CL">some words of DL's deleted by Charles</del>.
<lb/><subst><del hand="#CL" n="CL">some words</del><add hand="#CL" n="CL" place="over-text">overwritten by Charles</add></subst>

</p> 
            </div>
           
<div hand="#CL" n="CL">

<pb facs="liv_000101_0158.jpg" n="0158"/>
<lb/><p><fw><add place="inspace" hand="#U1" rend="gray right">150</add></fw>
<lb/>Return to a div in Charles's hand
<lb/>with <add place="below" hand="#DL" n="DL">^</add> <add place="above" hand="#DL" n="DL">some words of DL's words added above.</add>
<lb/>Here, there are some words <del type="strikethrough" hand="#DL" n="DL">of Charles's deleted by Livingstone</del> and then a few words <subst><del hand="#DL" n="DL">of CL's which are</del><add place="over-text" hand="#DL" n="DL">substituted by DL</add></subst>
<lb/>And then we have a portion of text <metamark function="flag" resp="#DL" n="DL" spanTo="#meta-236"/>flagged by DL<anchor xml:id="meta-236"/>
<lb/>And the rare instance of DL's words <add place="above" hand="#DL" n="DL" rend="gray">written in gray</add>
</p>
